Gosaiji graduation fin ending translation: he visits her at her new place after graduation. He says he never wants to leave this room and she says you returning to being a hikimori again. She adds at the end if he graduate properly this time she will live with him.
Homunculus a few days ago and now Napata? LETS GOOOO

@xDDDrocket: same, that 'Graduation Reward' story had me interested. For other ppl here is part 1: https://nhentai.net/g/344611/ [][][][]@takagi305: LOL nah, Napata's art just has a different flavor and a 'beauty' in itself bruh.

Looking forward to the translation for Gosaiji's Reward sequel. The male lead is independent enough that he doesn't turn into a self insert, but still sympathetic enough that I'm rooting for him. It's a nice balance between generic hentai mc, and ntr man. It's a sweet story. The art is S tier. But past generic qualities, I  think the facial expressions tell so much of the story and reflect the character dynamics. Male anatomy also manages to be useful in a vanilla manga, mc's weakness is captured in his sickly body, but expresses just enough of a thin layer of fat in some areas to show that he has an appetite and not expose us to the total turnoff of a skeleton. It's a nice change of pace from the usual featureless body and face of males that don't match their female counterparts.
